ir pesky cars will not gum up the works.\", \"from\": 3178, \"to\": 3277, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3206, \"to\": 3212}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3230}, {\"ngram\": \"their pesky cars\", \"from\": 3234, \"to\": 3250}, {\"ngram\": \"the works\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3276}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are LOTS of problem with that.\", \"from\": 3279, \"to\": 3315, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"problem\", \"from\": 3297, \"to\": 3304}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Healthcare: There are a great many folks who work at hospitals, clinics, and urgent care who have to DRIVE to get to work.\", \"from\": 3317, \"to\": 3439, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Healthcare\", \"from\": 3317, \"to\": 3327}, {\"ngram\": \"a great many folks\", \"from\": 3339, \"to\": 3357}, {\"ngram\": \"hospitals\", \"from\": 3370, \"to\": 3379}, {\"ngram\": \"clinics\", \"from\": 3381, \"to\": 3388}, {\"ngram\": \"urgent care\", \"from\": 3394, \"to\": 3405}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can better believe they will not be ditching their cars.\", \"from\": 3440, \"to\": 3500, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their cars\", \"from\": 3489, \"to\": 3499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Public Safety: Same goes.\", \"from\": 3502, \"to\": 3527, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You want cops keeping order, paramedics on tap if there is a crisis, or firefighters on the job?\", \"from\": 3528, \"to\": 3624, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cops\", \"from\": 3537, \"to\": 3541}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 3550, \"to\": 3555}, {\"ngram\": \"paramedics\", \"from\": 3557, \"to\": 3567}, {\"ngram\": \"tap\", \"from\": 3571, \"to\": 3574}, {\"ngram\": \"a crisis\", \"from\": 3587, \"to\": 3595}, {\"ngram\": \"firefighters\", \"from\": 3600, \"to\": 3612}, {\"ngram\": \"the job\", \"from\": 3616, \"to\": 3623}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yeah, they will be driving to work.\", \"